msgid "Advanced & Lab Features"
msgstr "進階與實驗室功能"

msgid "Beta"
msgstr "測試"

msgid "Full Software Backup & Restore"
msgstr "全量軟體的備份與還原"

msgid "Resolves traditional backup soft-brick risks. Smart backup is cross-version compatible. After flashing new firmware, upload backup to <span style=\"color:#ef4444; font-weight:bold;\">rapidly reinstall all software and losslessly restore configs (Requires Internet)</span>. Does not delete current software during restore. For absolute purity, factory reset the router first.<br><span style=\"color:#ef4444; font-weight:bold;\">Tip: If the backup shows Missing packages, manually place the installation packages in the /etc/netwiz/custom_pkgs/ directory.</span><br>If Netwiz is missing after a reset or needs an upgrade, connect to the internet and run this in SSH:"
msgstr "解決傳統備份容易導致當機、軟磚風險，智能備份（需聯網）<span style=\"color:#ef4444; font-weight:bold;\">相容跨版本還原（不能跨硬體）</span>。刷入新韌體後，上傳備份即可<span style=\"color:#ef4444; font-weight:bold;\">極速重裝所有軟體並無損還原設定</span>。還原時不會刪除當前軟體。若需達到絕對純淨，請先還原原廠設定。<br><span style=\"color:#ef4444; font-weight:bold;\">「提示：若備份中顯示“缺失安裝包（未備妥）”，請手動將安裝包放置於 /etc/netwiz/custom_pkgs/ 目錄下。」</span><br>恢復出廠後若未安裝 Netwiz 或需要陞級，可聯網後在 SSH 終端執行以下命令："

msgid "Generate Backup"
msgstr "產生備份檔案"

msgid "Restore System"
msgstr "還原系統軟體"

msgid "Click to Copy"
msgstr "點擊複製"

msgid "Copied"
msgstr "已複製"

msgid "Copy Failed"
msgstr "複製失敗"

msgid "Select Backup Mode"
msgstr "選擇備份模式"

msgid "Lightweight Backup"
msgstr "輕量化備份"

msgid "Recommended"
msgstr "推薦模式"

msgid "Full Backup"
msgstr "全量備份"

msgid "Includes Dependencies"
msgstr "包含深層依賴"

msgid "<b style=\"color: #F00;\">Lightweight Backup:</b> Only packs core configs (Passwords/Wi-Fi/IP) and main plugin packages. Fast and requires no extra RAM. Requires internet or built-in dependencies when restoring."
msgstr "<b style=\"color: #F00;\">輕量化備份說明:</b> 僅打包核心設定(帳號密碼/無線/IP)和主外掛包，不抓取底層深層依賴，速度極快。還原時新韌體需自帶對應依賴或處於聯網狀態。"

msgid "<b style=\"color: #F00;\">Full Backup:</b> Packs core configs and recursively downloads ALL underlying dependencies for third-party plugins. Large size, slower generation. <b style=\"color: #F00;\">NO internet required</b> during restore. Recommended for devices with >256MB RAM."
msgstr "<b style=\"color: #F00;\">全量備份說明:</b> 下載所有第三方外掛的完整底層依賴。體積龐大生成較慢，優點是還原時<b style=\"color: #F00;\">完全不需要網路</b>即可重裝成功。建議記憶體 >256M 的設備使用。"

msgid "Start Backup"
msgstr "確定開始備份"

msgid "Generating Backup"
msgstr "正在產生備份"

msgid "Extracting configs and packing files in background..."
msgstr "正在後台提取設定並打包檔案..."

msgid "Note: Full mode selected, downloading all dependencies. Takes 1-3 mins, please wait."
msgstr "提示: 當前為全量模式，需要下載全部底層依賴。大約需 1 到 3 分鐘，請耐心等待。"

msgid "Note: Lightweight mode selected, packing is very fast (~30s)."
msgstr "提示: 當前為輕量模式，打包速度極快。大約需要 30 秒左右。"

msgid "Backup Successful"
msgstr "打包成功"

msgid "Backup capsule downloaded. Upload this file after flashing new firmware to restore."
msgstr "備份膠囊已成功下載。刷入新系統後上傳此檔案即可還原。"

msgid "Backup Failed"
msgstr "打包失敗"

msgid "Unable to start background backup task."
msgstr "無法啟動後台備份任務"

msgid "Confirm System Restore"
msgstr "確認還原系統"

msgid "<span style=\"color:#ef4444; font-weight:bold;\">WARNING: This will overwrite current configs and reinstall plugins!</span><br><br>Router will auto-reboot upon completion. Ensure file is correct.<br><br><span style=\"color:#059669; font-size: 14px;\">"
msgstr "<span style=\"color:#ef4444; font-weight:bold;\">警告：此操作將覆蓋現有的網路設定並重新安裝外掛！</span><br><br>完成後路由器將自動重啟，請確保選擇的檔案無誤。<br><br><span style=\"color:#059669; font-size: 14px;\">"

msgid "Safe Mode: Auto-rollback if connection is lost for 300s.</span><br><br>"
msgstr "安全機制：若重啟後失聯 300 秒，系統將自動回退配置以防變磚。</span><br><br>"

msgid "Auto-download current state backup before restore (Regret Pill)"
msgstr "恢復前自動下載目前狀態備份 (後悔藥)"

msgid "Confirm & Select File"
msgstr "確認並選擇檔案"

msgid "Native Fast Restore Mode"
msgstr "原生極速還原模式"

msgid "Transferring capsule via high-speed system channel...<br><br><b style=\"color:#ef4444;\">DO NOT power off. Router will auto-reboot upon completion.</b><br><br><span style=\"color:#059669; font-size: 14px;\">"
msgstr "正在呼叫系統底層高速通道直傳膠囊...<br><br><b style=\"color:#ef4444;\">請勿斷開電源，路由器將在完成後自動重啟。</b><br><br><span style=\"color:#059669; font-size: 14px;\">"

msgid "Safe Mode: Auto-rollback if connection is lost for 300s.</span>"
msgstr "安全機制：若重啟後失聯 300 秒，系統將自動回退配置以防變磚。</span>"

msgid "Capsule delivered, preparing offline task..."
msgstr "膠囊已送達底層，準備執行脫機任務..."

msgid "Restore Blocked by Security"
msgstr "還原異常被安全攔截"

msgid "Self-healing mechanism triggered. Garbage cleared, router is safe and unharmed."
msgstr "系統已啟動自癒機制清理了垃圾殘留，您的路由器目前處於安全狀態，並未受損。"

msgid "Transfer Failed"
msgstr "傳輸失敗"

msgid "Interface rejected reception, status code: "
msgstr "底層接口拒絕接收，狀態碼: "

