msgstr "檢測到您的全量膠囊大小為 <b style=\"color:#ef4444;\">{size} MB</b>。<br><br>但當前路由器的 /tmp (運行記憶體) 僅剩餘 <b style=\"color:#ef4444;\">{avail} MB</b> 可用空間！<br><br>強行上傳將<b style=\"color:#f00;\">導致路由器記憶體溢出、當機並斷網</b>。<br><br><b>解決方案：</b>請先<b style=\"color:#10b981;\">重啟一次路由器</b>來清空記憶體碎片，重啟後再進行還原操作。"

msgid "Cancel Restore"
msgstr "取消還原"

msgid "Waiting for background task to start..."
msgstr "等待後台任務啟動..."

msgid "Capsule delivered, initializing restore environment..."
msgstr "膠囊已送達，正在初始化還原環境..."

msgid "Scanning capsule structure to estimate uncompressed size (5-10s)..."
msgstr "正在掃描膠囊深層結構以預估解壓體積 (約需 5-10 秒)..."

msgid "Uncompressed size reaches {u}MB, but RAM only has {a}MB left! Intercepted to prevent router crash."
msgstr "解壓體積達 {u}MB，但記憶體僅剩 {a}MB！為防止當機，已觸發安全攔截。"

msgid "Size safe! Extracting backup capsule..."
msgstr "體積安全！正在解壓備份膠囊..."

msgid "Extraction failed! Capsule may be corrupted, initiating self-healing..."
msgstr "解壓失敗！可能是壓縮包損壞，已啟動自癒機制清理記憶體。"

msgid "Extraction successful, applying core configs..."
msgstr "解壓成功，正在覆蓋系統核心設定..."

msgid "Force offline installing plugins (this takes a while, please wait)..."
msgstr "正在強制離線覆蓋外掛 (此過程較長，請耐心等待)..."

msgid "Restore thoroughly complete! Router will auto-reboot!"
msgstr "還原徹底完成！路由器即將自動重啟！"

msgid "MSG_RST_INVALID"
msgstr "無效的膠囊檔案！系統未檢測到 NetWiz 專屬特徵碼，為保護系統安全已自動攔截並銷毀。"

msgid "File Too Large"
msgstr "檔案過大"

msgid "<div style=\"text-align:left; color:#ef4444; font-weight:bold;\">Config files are usually under 100KB!</div><br>The selected file is too large and has been blocked."
msgstr "<div style=\"text-align:left; color:#ef4444; font-weight:bold;\">配置檔案通常小於 100KB！</div><br>您選擇的檔案過大，已被安全攔截。"

