msgstr "還原網路配置"

msgid "This action will overwrite the existing network configuration and restart the network.<br><br><span style=\"color:#f59e0b; font-weight:bold;\">"
msgstr "此操作將覆蓋現有的網路設定並重啟網路。<br><br><span style=\"color:#f59e0b; font-weight:bold;\">"

msgid "Security Warning: Do not upload backups from unknown sources to prevent router hijacking.</span><br><br>Confirm restore?"
msgstr "安全警告：請勿上傳來源不明的備份，以防路由器被劫持。</span><br><br>確認還原？"

