msgstr "您上傳的檔案不是有效的 JSON 格式，無法解析！"

msgid "Import Configuration"
msgstr "匯入配置"

msgid "Are you sure you want to import this configuration? Existing data will be overwritten."
msgstr "確認要匯入該配置嗎？現有資料將被徹底覆蓋。"

msgid "Severe Network Topology Conflict!"
msgstr "嚴重網路拓撲衝突！"

msgid "System detected that IPv6 and LAN \"Masquerading (NAT)\" are <b>BOTH enabled</b>!This will paralyze IPv6 allocation and cause routing loops.<br>👉 <b>Fix:</b> Please go to <code>Network -> Firewall</code> to disable LAN Masquerading, or <b style=\"color:#ef4444;\">Disable IPv6</b> in the LAN settings on the Netwiz homepage."
msgstr "系統檢測到 IPv6 與 LAN 區「動態偽裝 (NAT)」<b>同時處於開啟狀態</b>！這將導致 IPv6 分配癱瘓與路由死循環。<br>👉 <b>排錯指南：</b>請前往官方 <code>網路->防火牆</code> 關閉 LAN 區的動態偽裝，或在Netwiz首頁的區域網路設置裡 <b style=\"color:#ef4444;\">關閉 IPv6</b>。"

msgid "IPv6 Configuration Blocked"
msgstr "IPv6 配置已被系統安全攔截"

msgid "System detected that IPv6 and LAN \"Masquerading (NAT)\" are <b>BOTH enabled</b>!This will paralyze IPv6 allocation and cause routing loops.<br>"
msgstr "系統檢測到 IPv6 和區域網「IP 動態偽裝 (NAT)」<b>同時開啟</b>！這將導致 IPv6 分配癱瘓並引發路由環路。<br>"

msgid "<b>Fix:</b> Please go to <code>Network -> Firewall</code> to disable LAN Masquerading, or <b style=\"color:#ef4444;\">Disable IPv6</b> in the LAN settings on the Netwiz homepage."
msgstr "<b>修復建議：</b>請前往 <code>網路 -> 防火牆</code> 關閉區域網動態偽裝，或者在 Netwiz 首頁的區域網設定中<b style=\"color:#ef4444;\">關閉 IPv6</b>。"

msgid "Restore Device Data"
msgstr "還原設備資料"

msgid "This action will overwrite existing device groups and static IP bindings, and restart the network.<br><br><span style=\"color:#f59e0b; font-weight:bold;\">"
msgstr "此操作將覆蓋現有的設備分組和靜態 IP 綁定，並重啟網路。<br><br><span style=\"color:#f59e0b; font-weight:bold;\">"

msgid "Security Warning: Do not upload backups from unknown sources to prevent DNS hijacking.</span><br><br>Confirm to restore?"
msgstr "安全警告：請勿上傳來源不明的備份，以防 DNS 被劫持。</span><br><br>確認還原？"

msgid "Success"
msgstr "成功"

msgid "Warning"
msgstr "警告"

msgid "Waking up..."
msgstr "喚醒中..."

msgid "Displaying self-assigned local IPv6 as IPv4 is unavailable"
msgstr "由於無法獲取 IPv4，顯示設備底層自簽的區域 IPv6"

msgid "Local IPv6"
msgstr "自簽 IPv6"

msgid "System is rebooting, please wait..."
msgstr "系統重啟中，請稍候..."

msgid "Waiting for device to disconnect..."
msgstr "等待設備斷開連接..."

msgid "IP Conflict Warning"
msgstr "IP 衝突警告"

msgid "is already used by another device!"
msgstr "已被區域網內其他設備佔用！"

msgid "We strongly recommend changing it to avoid network crashes."
msgstr "強烈建議更改為新 IP，以防止網路癱瘓或斷網。"

msgid "Fix to"
msgstr "一鍵修復為"

msgid "Scanning installed plugins..."
msgstr "正在掃描已安裝的插件清單..."

msgid "Plugin Backup Status"
msgstr "插件備份狀態檢查"

msgid "Please verify backup packages:"
msgstr "請核對備份安裝包："

msgid "If you proceed, missing plugins WILL NOT be restored automatically!"
msgstr "如果現在執行備份，缺失安裝包在還原時將無法被恢復！"

msgid "Tip: Manually place missing packages .ipk/.apk into the /etc/netwiz/custom_pkgs/ directory via SSH to ensure they are automatically reinstalled during future restorations."
msgstr "建議：透過 SSH 將缺失的安裝包 .ipk 或 .apk 放入 /etc/netwiz/custom_pkgs/ 目錄，還原時會自動恢復當前狀態。"

msgid "Ignore & Backup"
msgstr "忽略並備份"

msgid "Missing packages:"
msgstr "缺失安裝包（未備妥）："

msgid "Manually placed in custom_pkgs:"
msgstr "手動放入 custom_pkgs 插件："

msgid "Custom Plugins Ready"
msgstr "自定義插件已就緒"

msgid "Great! Your custom plugins are safely stored in the local directory and will be included in the backup capsule."
msgstr "恭喜！已將所有自訂外掛離線包存入本地保險箱，後續將統一包裝封裝進備份膠囊。"

msgid "Confirm Backup"
msgstr "確定備份"

msgid "Auto-backup plugins:"
msgstr "可自動備份插件："

msgid "Plugin Scan Complete"
msgstr "插件掃描完成"

msgid "System scan complete! All your installed plugins are from the official repository and will be safely recorded for automatic restoration."
msgstr "系統掃描完畢！您安裝的所有第三方可視化插件，均存在於當前軟體源中。它們將被安全記錄並在未來自動聯網恢復。"

msgid "Backup Interrupted Warning"
msgstr "備份中斷警告"

msgid "Out of Memory (OOM Protection)!"
msgstr "記憶體不足 (OOM 預防機制)！"

msgid "The files you are trying to pack are too large and exceed the available memory.<br><br>To prevent device crash, the backup task has been safely canceled. Please clear unnecessary core files and try again."
msgstr "您要打包的檔案體積過大，超過了路由器當前的可用記憶體。<br><br>為防止設備死機，備份任務已自動安全取消。請嘗試清理無用的核心檔案後重試。"

msgid "I Got It"
msgstr "我知道了"

msgid "Scan Timeout Warning"
msgstr "掃描超時警告"

msgid "Communication Timeout or Network Error"
msgstr "通訊超時或網路異常"

msgid "Communication with the router timed out (possibly due to slow network source retrieval or network fluctuations).<br><br>To ensure backup integrity, the task has been safely canceled. Please try again later, or manually run opkg update via SSH."
msgstr "與路由器的通訊超時 (可能是網路源拉取過慢或網路波動)。<br><br>為保證備份完整性，任務已安全取消。請稍後再試，或在 SSH 中手動執行 opkg update。"

msgid "Connecting..."
msgstr "正在連接..."

msgid "Connecting to upstream... (Check password or signal strength if stuck)"
msgstr "正在連接上級網路... (若一直連接不上請檢查密碼是否正確或是否上級訊號太弱)"

msgid "First Time Syncing"
msgstr "首次核實插件清單"

msgid "Syncing lists in the background..."
msgstr "正在後台拉取最新列表..."

msgid "Verifying the list of plugins for automatic backup...<br><br>Depending on the network, this usually takes <b>15 to 20 seconds</b>.<br>The system is verifying, please wait..."
msgstr "正在核實可以自動備份的插件清單...<br><br>受限於網路，這通常需要 <b>15 ~ 20秒</b>。<br>系統正在核實，請稍候..."

msgid "OK, I will try again later"
msgstr "停止備份"

msgid "RESTORE FAILED: Package manager mismatch (apk vs ipk). Please use firmware with the same underlying system."
msgstr "恢復失敗：套件管理員格式衝突！您的備份包與當前系統的底層不相容（apk 與 ipk 衝突），強行恢復將導致系統損壞，進程已被系統強制攔截！"

msgid "RESTORE FAILED: CPU Architecture mismatch. Forcing this restore will brick your router! Process aborted."
msgstr "恢復致命攔截：CPU 架構不匹配！您正在嘗試將其他架構的備份強行刷入當前路由器，這會導致路由器徹底變磚！系統已自動終止恢復進程。"

msgid "Package Manager Conflict"
msgstr "軟體包管理器衝突"

msgid "CPU Architecture Conflict"
msgstr "CPU 架構衝突"

msgid "Your current system uses the apk architecture, but you are trying to flash an ipk backup!"
msgstr "您當前的系統使用 apk 架構，但您正嘗試刷入一個 ipk 格式的備份包！"

msgid "Your current system uses the opkg architecture, but you are trying to flash an apk backup!"
msgstr "您當前的系統使用 opkg 架構，但您正嘗試刷入一個 apk 格式的備份包！"

msgid "Architecture Warning"
msgstr "架構標識未匹配"

msgid "No architecture identifier ({arch}) detected in the selected backup filename."
msgstr "您選中的備份包名稱中，未檢測到當前路由器的架構標識 ({arch})。"

msgid "If you have <b>manually renamed</b> this file, please ignore this warning.<br><br><span style=\"color:#ef4444;\">If it is the wrong package, the system's underlying security mechanism will forcibly intercept the restoration later!</span>"
msgstr "如果您<b>手動修改過</b>該備份包的檔案名稱，請忽略此警告。<br><br><span style=\"color:#ef4444;\">如果您選錯了包，稍後的強行恢復將會被系統底層安全機制強制攔截！</span>"

msgid "I understand, continue"
msgstr "我知道了，繼續"

msgid "Scan to Connect"
msgstr "手機相機掃碼直連"

msgid "Architecture Safety Lock: Cross-package manager restoration (e.g., IPK to APK) is strictly prohibited. The underlying network and firewall configurations differ significantly across these system versions. Forcing a restore will cause severe network failure and brick your router!"
msgstr "架構安全鎖：嚴禁跨軟體包管理器（如 IPK 備份至 APK 系統）進行恢復！由於新舊系統的網路與防火牆底層設定格式存在重大差異，強行恢復設定將導致路由器直接斷網變磚！為了您的設備安全，系統已強制攔截此次操作。"

msgid "Force Restore Config"
msgstr "強制恢復設定"

msgid "Current WAN is in Secondary Router mode. PPPoE dial-up will not take effect until applied."
msgstr "目前 WAN 埠為二級路由模式，本頁套用設定前 PPPoE 撥號資訊無效。"

msgid "Current WAN is in PPPoE mode. Secondary Router mode will not take effect until applied."
msgstr "目前 WAN 埠為主路由的 PPPoE 撥號，本頁套用設定前二級路由模式無效。"

msgid "Advanced Utilities"
msgstr "高級實用設定"

msgid "MAC Address Clone"
msgstr "MAC 位址複製"

msgid "Scheduled Reboot"
msgstr "定時重啟設定"

msgid "Allow WAN Web Access"
msgstr "允許外網訪問後台，外網埠："

msgid "<b>Tip:</b> Some ISPs or campus networks bind to a specific device MAC. If dial-up fails, enter the cloned MAC here."
msgstr "<b>提示：</b>部分社區寬頻或校園網綁定了特定的設備 MAC（如舊路由器或電腦）。若撥號失敗，請在此填入該 MAC 進行偽裝複製。"

msgid "Auto-fill MAC"
msgstr "一鍵填寫 MAC"

msgid "No active device connection detected, please enter MAC address manually."
msgstr "未偵測到活動的設備連接，請手動輸入 MAC 位址。"

msgid "Enable Scheduled Reboot"
msgstr "啟用定時重啟路由器功能"

msgid "Reboot Time:"
msgstr "重啟時間:"

msgid "Repeat Days (Multi-select):"
msgstr "重複星期 (可多選):"

msgid "Please select at least one day!"
msgstr "請至少選擇一天！"

msgid "Mon"
msgstr "一"

msgid "Tue"
msgstr "二"

msgid "Wed"
msgstr "三"

msgid "Thu"
msgstr "四"

msgid "Fri"
msgstr "五"

msgid "Sat"
msgstr "六"

msgid "Sun"
msgstr "日"

msgid "Scheduled Reboot"
msgstr "定時重啟"

msgid "MAC Clone"
msgstr "MAC 複製"

msgid "Clear (Restore Default)"
msgstr "清空(恢復預設)"

msgid "Internet Connected"
msgstr "網際網路已連線"

msgid "Internet Disconnected"
msgstr "網際網路未連線"

msgid "Ignore"
msgstr "略過"

msgid "Invalid MAC address format!"
msgstr "MAC 位址格式不正確，請檢查！"

msgid "e.g., AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF"
msgstr "例如：AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF"

msgid "Multi-WAN detected. You can modify the account and password for each line separately (other settings remain unchanged)."
msgstr "系統偵測到多線撥號環境，可分別修改各線路的帳號密碼（其他設定保持不變）。"

msgid "Interface:"
msgstr "線路介面:"

msgid "Multi-WAN detected. Only the primary WAN will be configured here, other lines remain unchanged."
msgstr "系統偵測到多線環境，向導中僅配置主線路 (WAN)，其餘線路將保持原樣。"

msgid "Custom Hosts"
msgstr "自訂 Hosts"

msgid "Custom <a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" id=\"nw-hosts-raw-toggle\" style=\"color:red; text-decoration:underline dashed; transition:color 0.2s;\" title=\"Click to toggle pure text advanced mode\">Hosts</a>"
msgstr "自訂 <a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" id=\"nw-hosts-raw-toggle\" style=\"color:red; text-decoration:underline dashed; transition:color 0.2s;\" title=\"點擊切換純文本高級模式\">Hosts</a>"

msgid "(Domain Hijack)"
msgstr "(網域劫持)"

msgid "Quick Add:"
msgstr "快速新增紀錄:"

msgid "Add"
msgstr "新增"

msgid "No custom Hosts, please add below."
msgstr "暫無自訂 Hosts，請點擊上方新增紀錄"

msgid "IP (e.g., 127.0.0.1 or ::1)"
msgstr "指向 IP (127.0.0.1 或 ::1)"

msgid "Domain (e.g., router.lan)"
msgstr "劫持網域 (如 router.lan)"

msgid "Comment (Optional)"
msgstr "備註說明 (選填)"

msgid "<b>Pure Text Mode</b>: <b>Paste</b> to import, <b>Copy</b> to export. Format: <code>IP Domain #Comment</code>"
msgstr "<b>純文字模式</b>：<b>貼上</b>匯入，<b>全選複製</b>可匯出保存到txt。格式：<code>IP 網域 #備註</code>"

msgid "IP and Domain cannot be empty!"
msgstr "IP 和 網域 不能為空！"

msgid "Invalid IP address format!"
msgstr "IP 位址格式不正確！"

msgid "Invalid domain! Spaces, wildcards (*), and special characters are not allowed."
msgstr "網域格式不正確！不支援泛解析(*)，且不允許包含空格或特殊危險字元。"

msgid "No changes have been made."
msgstr "您沒有進行任何修改！"

msgid "Notice"
msgstr "提示訊息"

msgid "This IP and Domain combination already exists!"
msgstr "此 IP 和 網域的組合已經存在，請勿重複新增！"

msgid "Duplicate records found in Hosts! Please remove them before continuing."
msgstr "Hosts文件中發現重複的 IP+網域 規則！請手動刪除重複項後再試。"

msgid "Smart Auto-fill"
msgstr "智能補全"

msgid "Auto-fill IPv4/v6 & www domain combinations"
msgstr "自動生成 IPv4/v6 以及帶 www 和不帶 www 的組合規則"

msgid "This feature forces specific domains to resolve to designated IPs. Commonly used for blocking domain access or local device redirection."
msgstr "此功能可制將特定網域強解析到指定的 IP 位址。常用於阻止某網域連網 或 區域網路設備重定向。"

msgid "Found invalid or duplicate records:"
msgstr "在純文字中發現了格式錯誤或重複的記錄，共計："

msgid "Click [OK] to automatically discard them and continue, or [Cancel] to manually fix them."
msgstr "點擊【確定】將自動捨棄錯誤項並保存，點擊【取消】則返回手動修改。"

msgid "Plugin Repair"
msgstr "插件修復"

msgid "Please wait"
msgstr "請稍候"

msgid "Scanning for repairable plugins..."
msgstr "正在掃描可修復的插件清單..."

msgid "Standard uninstallation does not remove plugin configuration files. If a plugin malfunctions after reinstallation, select it below to reset it to its initial state."
msgstr "常規卸載不會清除插件設定檔。若插件重裝後仍無法正常使用，可在下方選中對應插件，將其重置為初始狀態。"

msgid "Factory Default"
msgstr "出廠預設值"

msgid "Plugin Repair Toolkit"
msgstr "插件修復急救箱"

msgid "Repair Now"
msgstr "立即修復"

msgid "Processing"
msgstr "處理中"

msgid "Repairing and restarting"
msgstr "正在修復並且重啟"

msgid " please wait"
msgstr " 請稍候"

msgid "Repair Successful"
msgstr "修復成功"

msgid "has been successfully restored"
msgstr "已經成功恢復"

msgid "Repair Failed"
msgstr "修復失敗"

msgid "Unable to repair this plugin"
msgstr "無法修復該插件"

msgid "System Error"
msgstr "系統異常"

msgid "Request timeout or error"
msgstr "請求超時或者出錯"

msgid "Notice"
msgstr "提示"

msgid "No repairable plugins found"
msgstr "沒有找到可以修復的插件"

msgid "Failed to get plugin list"
msgstr "獲取插件清單失敗"

msgid "Port number must be between 1 and 65535"
msgstr "埠號必須介於 1 到 65535 之間"

msgid "For system security, do not use"
msgstr "為了系統安全請勿使用"

msgid "as the external port. It is a reserved high-risk port."
msgstr "作為外網埠號此為系統保留高危險埠號"

msgid "It is recommended to use 8080 or a port above 10000."
msgstr "建議使用 8080 或 10000 以上的埠號"

msgid "Enter custom external port number"
msgstr "填寫自訂外網埠號"

msgid "Port"
msgstr "通訊埠衝突：通訊埠"

msgid "is already in use by another application!"
msgstr "已被其他服務佔用！"
